title: Dead Sonja - She Zombie With A Sword  (2006) (Digital) (Empire).
description:
Dead Sonja - She Zombie With A Sword  (2006) (Digital) (Empire) 


50 pages! A brain-devouring blatant spoof spectacular, right in time for Halloween! After her family is killed and she is taken advantage of by a pack of evil zombie mercenaries, young Dead Sonja is granted sword-wielding zombie superpowers by a mysterious undead Goddess! Vowing to never lay with another zombie man unless defeated in fair zombie combat, Dead Sonja wanders the mythic land of long ago, takin' names and eatin' brains. The biggest zombie party of all-time starts here!
